org.kahina.core.gui.menus

Class KahinaProjectMenuListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kahina.core.gui.menus.KahinaProjectMenuListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.util.EventListener

    public class KahinaProjectMenuListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener
    A default listener for the project menu, only creates and dispatches KahinaProjectEvents by default. Can be specialized by applications. Instead of overriding the actionPerformed method, it might be more straightforward to override the provided convenience methods.
